data.description: Hard to find single level home in Boise. This 4 bedroom (or 3 with an office) home has an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings in the great room. Spacious primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings and jetted tub. Large three car garage. Patio built for entertaining.  Formal living area. Hidden shelving in garage. Low maintenance backyard with fire pit.
